    <h3>RAG-Powered AI Tutors</h3>
    <p>
        AI Knowledge Companion leverages <strong>Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)</strong> to create intelligent tutors 
        that answer questions based on your uploaded materials. The system automatically chunks documents, generates vector 
        embeddings using OpenAI's text-embedding-3-small model, and performs semantic similarity search to retrieve the most 
        relevant context for each query. Users can fine-tune RAG parameters including similarity threshold (0.0-1.0), maximum 
        context chunks, and AI temperature to optimize responses for their specific use case.
    </p>
