    <h3>Multimedia Processing & Knowledge Base</h3>
    <p>
        The platform features <strong>advanced multimedia processing capabilities</strong> that transform any content type 
        into searchable knowledge. Audio and video files are automatically transcribed using OpenAI Whisper API, images are 
